item.title: DawgCTF 2021
item.description: foreword DawgCTF 20201 was the first CTF I played together with some local people much smarter than me over at Hack South. We managed to grab 28th place too. I only solved three challenges with the time I had in the morning (of which one was a dupe because reading is hard :P). solutions reversing - calculator Category: Reversing Points: 50 Files: Windows PE This was the duplicate challenge, but I’m writing up how I did it anyways.
